This software will show the speed of any SJ 2000
train that you might travel on. The data is 
retreaved from the onboard site. API information 
is found on: 
http://tagtider.net/blogg/utveckling/internet-ombord-api-med-tagkoordinater/
The software will show an incorrect speed if the
computer is not connected to the onboard SJ wifi.

====================================================
                      Installation
====================================================
1. Run the "SJ - Speed.exe"
2. You are done. 
3. Close with the cross.